        <updateDate>2020-11-06T17:31:02Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Fixing Global Freeloading Act </b></p> <p>This bill establishes the position of Chief Pharmaceutical Negotiator in the Office of the U.S. Trade Representative. The Chief Pharmaceutical Negotiator must conduct trade negotiations and enforce trade agreements related to pharmaceutical products and services. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
